room_title: Escape room "Secret in the Attic" by Escape Room Arlington in Arlington (VA)
room_address: 2301 Columbia Pike Suite C Arlington, VA 22204
room_description:
Everyone loves your Grandmother, including you. Baking cookies, knitting sweaters, and everything else on the good Grandmother checklist. But you've always felt that there was something off about her, she always seemed to have lived a life more adventurous than the stories told of her youth. 
After she passed away, you took it upon yourself to find out her secret. What was your sweet old Grandma hiding in the attic? The answer may change your life forever.
